  "title": "Junior KYC Officer (Foreign Bank) #BJT",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Review KYC information &amp; documents of clients</li>\n  <li>Conduct research in public domains and the bank’s data sources to validate the client profiles</li>\n  <li>Work with banker team to complete Periodic Review</li>\n  <li>Coordinate and liaise across businesses and compliance units for timely completion of Periodic Review</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Application Procedures</strong></p>\n<p>Interested candidates, please email your resume to:</p>\n<p>Attention: Jamie Tan Pei Zhen (CEI No. R2199473)</p>\n<p><strong>jamietan@recruitexpress.com.sg</strong></p>\n<p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd (EA No. 99C4599)</p>",
